title: Automation and Processing Test Data with LabVIEW Software
abstract: This paper presents the usage of LabVIEW software for automation of data acquisition and data post processing during structure testing. Using Labview could accelerate preparation of testing reports especially during performing repeatedly (obtaining statistics). The paper shows automations made during tests of oil tank models and aluminium bridge.
